ange of signaling outputs to TGFb ligand in\ndifferent cell types and under different conditions can be explained with\ndifferences in cellular protein concentrations and with changes in effective\nrate constants due to cross-talk with other signaling pathways.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2011 13:34:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2011 14:54:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-19"}
