rough imaging and spectroscopy to a few\npercent, in agreement with observational samples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2011 15:38:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Mar 2012 17:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-03-05"}
